o.com\/rooms-and-suites\/\">22 rooms and suites<\/a> is individually styled, inspired by the villa&#8217;s rich history, with bespoke details executed by local craftsmen and our in-house artisans using traditional techniques. Experience the <strong>ultimate luxury Tuscan vacation<\/strong> at Borgo Santo Pietro, your home away from home in Tuscany.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/ultimate-seclusion1.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - rooms &#038; suites\"><\/p>\n<h2>Rooms &#038; suites<\/h2>\n<p>Your luxury resort in Tuscany<\/p>\n<div>\n<p>your luxury resort in Tuscany<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><a href=\"\/rooms-and-suites\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Borgo-Santo-Pietro-Saporium_stars-2.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - food &#038; wine\"><\/p>\n<h2>Food &#038; wine<\/h2>\n<p>Farm-to-plate dining<\/p>\n<div>\n<p>farm-to-plate dining<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><a href=\"\/food-and-wine\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Borgo-Santo-Pietro-Saporium_stars-treatment-1.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - spa &#038; wellness\"><\/p>\n<h2>Spa &#038; wellness<\/h2>\n<p>Your holistic spa in Tuscany<\/p>\n<div>\n<p>your holistic spa in Tuscany<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><a href=\"\/luxury-spa-resort-tuscany\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Borgo-Santo-Pietro-Saporium_autumn2.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - gardens\"><\/p>\n<h2>Gardens<\/h2>\n<p>a hotel within a garden<\/p>\n<div>\n<p>a hotel within a garden<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><a href=\"\/gardens\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Borgo-Santo-Pietro-Saporium_sautunno.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - adventures\"><\/p>\n<h2>Experiences<\/h2>\n<p>Live the Tuscan dream<\/p>\n<div>\n<p>Live the Tuscan dream<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><a href=\"\/experiences-at-borgo\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/events.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - events &#038; offers\"><\/p>\n<h2>Events &#038; offers<\/h2>\n<p>Plan your Tuscan getaway<\/p>\n<div>\n<p>Plan your Tuscan getaway<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><a href=\"\/events-and-offers\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/ultimate-seclusion1.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - rooms &#038; suites\"><\/p>\n<h2>Rooms &#038; suites<\/h2>\n<p>Your luxury resort in Tuscany<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"\/rooms-and-suites\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Borgo-Santo-Pietro-Saporium_stars-2.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - food &#038; wine\"><\/p>\n<h2>Food &#038; wine<\/h2>\n<p>Farm-to-plate dining<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"\/food-and-wine\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Borgo-Santo-Pietro-Saporium_stars-treatment-1.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - spa &#038; wellness\"><\/p>\n<h2>Spa &#038; wellness<\/h2>\n<p>Your holistic spa in Tuscany<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"\/luxury-spa-resort-tuscany\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Borgo-Santo-Pietro-Saporium_autumn2.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - gardens\"><\/p>\n<h2>Gardens<\/h2>\n<p>A hotel within a garden<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"\/gardens\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Borgo-Santo-Pietro-Saporium_sautunno.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - experiences\"><\/p>\n<h2>Experiences<\/h2>\n<p>Live the Tuscan dream<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"\/experiences-at-borgo\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/events.jpg\" alt=\"borgo santo pietro - events &#038; offers\"><\/p>\n<h2>Events &#038; offers<\/h2>\n<p>Plan your Tuscan getaway<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"\/events-and-offers\/\"><\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Packages<\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Enjoy your stay at our 5 star luxury resort in Tuscany with curate packages that pair wellness and adventure with gourmet food and 5-star service for a fully immersive Borgo Santo Pietro experience.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Food &amp; wine<br \/><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>With our top-notch team of chefs, gardeners, local farmers and producers, we aim to deliver the best of Tuscan cuisine to your table. Our boutique wine selection embodies the same traditional principles of quality and discernment.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MICHELIN-2025_1-StarGreen-Star_Horizontal_Black.png\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Borgo Santo Pietro Saporium<\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Enjoy an innovative farm-to-plate experience in our restaurant in the heart of Tuscany.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><p>\n        <a href=\"\/food-and-wine\/restaurant\/\">More about the Restaurant<\/a>\n    <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Borgo-Santo-Pietro-Saporium-autumn.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Borgo Santo Pietro Saporium<\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Enjoy an innovative farm-to-plate experience in our Michelin-starred restaurant in the heart of Tuscany.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><p>\n        <a href=\"\/food-and-wine\/restaurant\/\">More about the Restaurant\u00a0<\/a>\n    <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<h3>Trattoria Sull\u2019Albero<\/h3>\n<div>Built around two oak trees, Trattoria Sull\u2019Albero offers menus that showcase our farm-to-plate philosophy, with 0km meat, fresh cheese and vegetables, free-range eggs and prosciutto sourced from the estate.\n<\/div>\n<p><p>\n        <a href=\"\/food-and-wine\/trattoria-sullalbero-restaurant\/\">More about La Trattoria<\/a>\n    <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/trattoria-topslider1.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Trattoria Sull\u2019Albero<\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Built around two oak trees, Trattoria Sull\u2019Albero offers menus that showcase our farm-to-plate philosophy, with 0km meat, fresh cheese and vegetables, free-range eggs and prosciutto sourced from the estate.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><p>\n        <a href=\"\/food-and-wine\/trattoria-sullalbero-restaurant\/\">More about La Trattoria<\/a>\n    <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<h3>Wine Cellar<\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Our wine cellar showcases 1500 labels from both Tuscan and Italian producers, whose passion for wine and time-honoured techniques faithfully reflect the terroir in which each wine is produced.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><p>\n        <a href=\"\/food-and-wine\/wine-cellar\/\">More about the wine cellar<\/a>\n    <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/winecellar-3rd-slider2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Wine Cellar<\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Our wine cellar showcases 1500 labels from both Tuscan and Italian producers, whose passion for wine and time-honoured techniques faithfully reflect the terroir in which each wine is produced.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><p>\n        <a href=\"\/food-and-wine\/wine-cellar\/\">More about the wine cellar<\/a>\n    <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<h3>The Borgo Cooking School<\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Set amidst the productive kitchen gardens, organic farmland, and vineyards of Borgo Santo Pietro, The Borgo Cooking School is a <strong>farm-to-plate cooking school in the heart of the Tuscany<\/strong>. With an extensive list of classes and cooking workshops, you can select from pizza\/pasta making with local cooks to advanced gourmet classes with Michelin-starred chefs or partake in artisan cheese-making workshop.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><p>\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/estate.borgosantopietro.com\/cooking-school\/\">More about the cooking school<\/a>\n    <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/borgo-cooking-school-2019-2-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"Borgo cooking school\"><\/p>\n<h3>The Borgo Cooking School<\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Set amidst the productive kitchen gardens, organic farmland, and vineyards of Borgo Santo Pietro, The Borgo Cooking School is <strong>a farm-to-plate cooking school in the heart of the Tuscany<\/strong>. With an extensive list of classes and cooking workshops, you can select from pizza\/pasta making with local cooks to advanced gourmet classes with Michelin-starred chefs or partake in artisan cheese-making workshop.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><p>\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/estate.borgosantopietro.com\/cooking-school\/\">More about the cooking school<\/a>\n    <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><br \/>\n<!-- {\"name\":\"Hotel - New content - 12\\\/09\\\/2019\",\"type\":\"layout\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Hotel Landing Desktop Slider\",\"type\":\"section\",\"props\":{\"class\":\"uk-visible@m uk-position-relative landing_slider\",\"header_transparent\":true,\"header_transparent_noplaceholder\":true,\"header_transparent_text_color\":\"light\",\"id\":\"main_slider\",\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"padding\":\"none\",\"style\":\"secondary\",\"title_breakpoint\":\"xl\",\"title_position\":\"top-left\",\"title_rotation\":\"left\",\"vertical_align\":\"\",\"width\":\"\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"row\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"column\",\"props\":{\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"position_sticky_breakpoint\":\"m\",\"width_medium\":\"1-1\"},\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Hotel Landing Desktop Slider\",\"type\":\"slideshow\",\"props\":{\"block_align\":\"center\",\"id\":\"landing_slider\",\"link_style\":\"default\",\"link_text\":\"Read more\",\"margin\":\"remove-vertical\",\"margin_remove_bottom\":true,\"margin_remove_top\":true,\"meta_align\":\"below-title\",\"meta_element\":\"div\",\"meta_style\":\"text-meta\",\"nav\":\"\",\"nav_align\":\"center\",\"nav_breakpoint\":\"s\",\"nav_position\":\"bottom-center\",\"nav_position_margin\":\"medium\",\"overlay_animation\":\"slide-right-small\",\"overlay_margin\":\"large\",\"overlay_